summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Pinellas Place from North 55th Street to Kenwood Place, et al in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete walks under Ordinance No. 18825, creating Local Improvement District No. 1811 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
